# CSS formatting

- Do not insert blank lines between properties inside a CSS rule block.
- Keep a single blank line between separate rule blocks.
- After editing any `.css` file, run: `uv run python scripts/format_css.py <path>`
- Do not run `ruff format` on CSS files; Ruff is for Python only.
- Pre-commit runs the CSS formatter automatically when hooks are installed.
